    "summary": {
      "value": "The powerful witch queen, teacher of dark arts."
    },
    "featureType": "projectfu.arcanum",
    "data": {
      "merge": "<h3>Haunting Dance</h3><p>After you and/or one or more allies you can see lose Hit Points, you gain <strong>1 Sorcery Point</strong>.</p><p>All damage you deal becomes <strong>poison</strong>, its type cannot change, and you deal extra damage equal to your current <strong>Sorcery Points</strong>.</p><p>When this Arcanum is dismissed, you lose all <strong>Sorcery Points</strong>.</p><hr><p><strong>You Gain:</strong> @PROGRESS[sorcery-points update 1]{Gain 1 Sorcery Point}</p>",
      "pulse": "",
      "dismiss": "<h3>Feast of Body and Soul</h3><p>You deal an amount of <strong>poison</strong> damage equal to <strong>【the amount of Sorcery Points you lost by dismissing this Arcanum, multiplied by 5】</strong> to one enemy you can see. If this damage reduces that enemy to 0 Hit Points, you and every ally you can see recover an amount of HP and MP equal to that enemy's <strong>Crisis</strong> score.</p><hr><p><strong>Enemy Suffers:</strong> @DMG[&cs('sorcery-points')*5+&step(0,10,20) poison]{Poison Damage}<br><strong>You Lose:</strong> @PROGRESS[sorcery-points reset]{Lose All Sorcery Points}</p>",
      "domains": "medicine, poisons, witchcraft"
    },
    "source": "FUBC36"
  },
